 Zaburi I 18:2 4, 13-15ab, 22-24 </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mshukuruni Bwana kwa kuwa ni mwema, kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Israeli na aseme sasa: wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nyumba ya Haruni iseme: wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wamchao Bwana waseme: wema wake ni wa milele. </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mshukuruni Bwana kwa kuwa ni mwema, kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nilisukumwa, nilisukumizwa nianguke, lakini Bwana amenisaidia.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ni nguvu na uhodari wangu,
yeye amekuwa wokovu wangu. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sauti ya shangwe na ya ushindi imo katika hema za watu waadilifu.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mshukuruni Bwana kwa kuwa ni mwema, kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jiwe walilolikataa waashi limekuwa jiwe kuu la pembeni.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jambo hili alilifanya Bwana; nalo ni la ajabu machoni petu. </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hii ndiyo siku aliyoifanya Bwana;
tuishangilie na kuifurahia. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mshukuruni Bwana kwa kuwa ni mwema, kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> SOMO LA PILI 
1 Petro 1:3-9 </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Petro</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atukuzwe Mungu, Baba wa Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo. </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huyo Baba ametuzaa upya kwa huruma yake kubwa, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tupate tumaini hai kwa ufufuko wa Yesu Kristo katika wafu; </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>pia tupate urithi usioharibika, wala kuchafuka, wala kufifia, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mliowekewa mbinguni. Nguvu ya Mungu inawahifadhi </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa sababu ya imani yenu, hata mpate wokovu ulio tayari </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kufunuliwa wakati wa mwisho. Hapo mtashangilia, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ijapo sasa imewapasa kuhuzunika kwa kitambo kidogo katika </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>majaribio kadha wa kadha. Wakati wa kufunuliwa Yesu Kristo, imani </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yenu iliyojaribiwa kama dhahabu iliyosafishwa kwa moto - </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ionekane ni bora zaidi kuliko dhahabu hafifu, mpate sifa na</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>utukufu na heshima. Mwampenda Kristo, ijapo hamjamwona bado, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na bila kumwona sasa, mnamsadiki. Mtamshangilia kwa furaha tukufu </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>isiyosemekana, yaani wakati mtakapokuwa mmefikia </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>upeo wa imani yenu, ndio wokovu wa roho zenu.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Neno la Bwana.
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI 
Yohane 20:29</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya. Aleluya.
Kwa kuwa umeniona, Tomaso, umesadiki. asema Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wenye heri wale wasioona na wakasadiki. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI 
Yohane 20:19-31</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane 
(UTUKUFU KWAKO, EE BWANA.)</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jioni ya siku ile ya kwanza ya juma, alikuja Yesu, akasimama katikati.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ingawa milango ya chumba 
walimokaa wafuasi ilikuwa imefungwa </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kuwaogopa Wayahudi, 
akawaambia, “Amani iwe nanyi.\" </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada ya maneno hayo, akawaonyesha mikono yake na ubavu wake. </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wafuasi wakafurahi walipomwona Bwana Yesu akawaambia mara ya pili, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Amani iwe nanyi. Kama Baba alivyonituma mimi, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nami nawatuma ninyi.\" Baada ya maneno hayo, akawapulizia, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akawaambia, \"Pokeeni Roho Mtakatifu. Wowote </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mtakaowaondolea dhambi, wameondolewa, </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wowote mtakaowafungia dhambi, wamefungiwa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini Tomaso, aitwaye Pacha, 
mmoja wa wale Kumi na Wawili, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hakuwako pamoja nao alipokuja Yesu. Basi, wafuasi wengine wakamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tumemwona Bwana.\" Yeye lakini akawajibu,\"Nisipoona matundu ya </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>misumari mikononi mwake, na kutia kidole changu sehemu za </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>misumari, na kutia mkono wangu katika ubavu wake, sisadiki hata kidogo,\" </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada ya siku nane, wafuasi wake walikuwamo tena chumbani, </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Tomaso pamoja nao. Akaja Yesu, ingawa milango ilikuwa imefungwa, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akasimama kati yao, akasema, \"Amani iwe nanyi.\" </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kisha akamwambia Tomaso, \"Tia kidole chako humu, tazama mikono yangu, </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lete mkono wako na kuutia katika ubavu wangu na usikose imani, </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali uwe anayeamini.\" Tomaso akajibu akamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Bwana wangu na Mungu wangu!\" 
Yesu akamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Kwa kuwa umeniona, umesadiki? Wenye heri wale wasioona </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wakasadiki,\" Sasa Yesu alifanya ishara nyingine nyingi mbele ya </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wafuasi wake zisizoandikwa katika kitabu hiki. Lakini hizi </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>zimeandikwa, mpate kusadiki ya kuwa Yesu ni Masiya, Mwana wa Mungu,</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tena kwa kusadiki mpate kuwa na uzima kwa jina lake.</s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana
(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
