Zaburi 4:2, 4,7, 9 (K. 7b) </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Ee Bwana, tuinulie mwanga wa uso wako! au: Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niitapo uniitikie, ee Mungu wa haki yangu. Wakati wa shida, umenipatia </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>njia; unionee huruma; usikilize sala yangu. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Ee Bwana, tuinulie mwanga wa uso wako! au: Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jueni ya kuwa Bwana hutenda maajabu kwa waamini wake; Bwana atasikia nimwitapo. </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Ee Bwana, tuinulie mwanga wa uso wako! au: Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wengi husema, 
Nani atakayetuonyesha mema!</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Bwana, tuinulie mwanga wa uso wako!\" </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Ee Bwana, tuinulie mwanga wa uso wako! au: Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa amani nitajilaza na kupata usingizi mara, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
