unaponena nasi. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI 
Luka 24:35-48</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka Wakati ule:</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(UTUKUFU KWAKO EE BWANA)</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule wafuasi wake wawili wa Emau walisimulia wale kumi na </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mmoja na wenzao yaliyowatukia njiani, na jinsi walivyomtambua [Yesu katika kuumega mkate. Walipokuwa wakisema bado mambo hay. [Yesu] Yesu</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika kuumega mkate.Walipokuwa wakisema bado mambo hayo, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu mwenyewe alisimama katikati akawaambia, \"Amani iwe nanyi\".</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Katika mahangaiko na hofu yao 
wakadhani wanaona mzimu.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
