Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mniguse na kuona. Mzimu hauna 
mwili na mifupa kama </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mnavyoniona kuwa nayo\". Baada ya maneno hayo, aliwaonyesha mikono na miguu.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Walishindwa bado kuamini kwa jinsi walivyofurahi na kushangaa.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi. akawaambia, \"Mna chakula chochote hapa?\" Wakampa kipande </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>cha samaki wa kuokwa. Akakitwaa, akala mbele yao. Kisha akawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Hii ndiyo maana ya maneno yangu 
niliyowaambia nilipokaa bado nanyi, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani, lazima yatimizwe yote yaliyoandikwa katika Sheria ya Musa, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na katika manabii na zaburi.\" Halafu akawafungulia akili wapate </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuyafahamu. Akawaambia,\"Ndivyo ilivyoandikwa, kwamba Kristo 
atateswa </s></f>"},{ID:61,
