Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>  kwa sababu mtumishi hajui atendalo bwana wake. </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nawaita rafiki, kwa kuwa nimewajulisha yote niliyoyasikia kwa Baba yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Si ninyi mlionichagua mimi, bali ni mimi niliyewachagua ninyi, kusudi mwende mkazae matunda,</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na matunda yenu yadumu, ili Baba awapeni lolote mwombalo kwa jina langu.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
