Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Petro altumbua kinywa, akasema, “Mmejua yaliyotukia </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika Uyahudi wote kuanzia Galilaya baada ya ubatizo aliohubiri Yohane, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu alivyompaka mafuta Yesu wa Nazareti kwa Roho Mtakatifu na nguvu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na jinsi alvyozunguka katika nchi yote akitenda mema na kuwaponya </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wote walioonewa na Shetani,
kwa maana Mungu alikuwa pamoja naye.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nasi ni mashahidi wa yote aliyoyafanya katika nchi ya Wayahudi </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na katika Yerusalemu. Naye walimtundika mtini na kumwua. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu lakini alimfufua siku ya tatu na kumjalia aonekane, si kwa watu wote, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ila kwa mashahidi waliokuwa wamechaguliwa na  Mungu, ndio sisi </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tuliokula na kunywa pamoja naye baada ya kufufuka kwake katika wafu.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndio sisi aliotuagiza tuwahubirie na kuwashuhudia watu kwamba: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huyu ndiye aliyewekwa na Mungu kuwahukumu wazima na wafu. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huyu manabii wote wameshuhudia, kwamba kila anayemsadiki </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>anaondolewa dhambi kwa jina lake.\"</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU) </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA 	
Zaburi 118:1-2,16ab-17, 22-23</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Hii ndiyo siku aliyoifanya Bwana. Tufurahi na tushangilie</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele. Israeli na aseme sasa
Wema wake ni wa milele. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Hii ndiyo siku aliyoifanya Bwana. Tufurahi na tushangilie</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mkono wa kuume wa Bwana umetukuzwa, mkono wa kuume wa Bwana umetenda makuu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sitakufa, bali nitaishi, nami nitayasimulia matendo ya Bwana. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Hii ndiyo siku aliyoifanya Bwana. Tufurahi na tushangilie</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jiwe walilokataa waashi limekuwa jiwe kuu la pembeni. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jambo hili alilifanya Bwana; nalo ni la ajabu machoni petu. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Hii ndiyo siku aliyoifanya Bwana. Tufurahi na tushangilie</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI 
Wakolosai 3:1-4</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakolosai</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Ikiwa mmefufuliwa pamoja na Kristo, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yatafuteni yaliyo juu anakokaa Kristo kuume kwa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zingatieni yaliyo juu, si mambo ya duniani. Maana mmekwisha kufa, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na uzima wenu umefichika pamoja na Kristo katika utukufu. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baadaye Kristo aliye uzima wetu atakapotokea, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ninyi pia mtatokea pamoja naye katika utukufu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Au lifuatalo:</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI      1 Wakorintho 5:6b-8</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Hamjui kwamba chachu kidogo huchachusha donge lote? </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, iondosheni chachu ya zamani, mpate kuwa donge jipya, ninyi  mlio watu msiochachuka.  </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana mwanakondoo wetu wa Pasaka ametolewa  sadaka, ndiye Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Haya, tuadhimishe sikukuu, si kwa chachu ya zamani, wala kwa chachu ya ubaya na uovu, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali kwa donge lisilochachuka, yaani la unyofu na ukweli.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Mungu. 
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SEKWENSIA</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristo Paska yetu amechinjwa sadaka, Tuile karamuye na twimbe aleluya</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aliyejitoa sadaka ya Paska 
Wakristo wamtolee sadaka ya sifa</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwanakondoo amewakomboa kondoo: Kristo asiye na dhambi </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amewapatanisha na Baba watu wenye dhambi.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mauti na uzima vimeshindana ajabu:
Mkuu wa uzima aliyekufa, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atawala mzima. Utuambie Maria, uliona nini njiani?</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niliona kaburi la Kristo mzima, na utukufu wa mwenye aliyekufa:</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mashahidi ni malaika, leso ya uso na mavazi. Kristo tumaini langu </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kafufuka:atawatangulia Galilaya.
Twajua Kristo amefufuka kweli </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika wafu: ewe Mfalme mshindaji, utuhurumie. Amina. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
1 Wakorintho 5:7b, 8a</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya. Aleluya
Kristo, Mwanakondoo wetu wa Pasaka, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ametolewa sadaka. Haya, tuadhimishe sikukuu katika Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Yn. 20:1-9</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika Injili ilivyoandikwa na Yohane.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku ya kwanza ya juma, Maria Magdalena  alifika kwenye kaburi asubuhi  sana, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kungali giza bado, na akaliona jiwe limeondolewa kaburini.   </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi akapiga mbio, akafika kwa Simoni Petro na yule mfuasi mwingine </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ambaye Yesu alimpenda, akawaambia, “Wamemwondoa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana kaburini, na sisi hatujui walikomweka.”</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Petro akatoka pamoja na yule mfuasi mwingine kwenda kaburini.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wote wawili walipiga mbio,lakini yule mfuasi mwingine alitangulia, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maana alikimbia mbio kuliko Petro,
akafika kwanza kwenye kaburi; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akainama na kuchungulia, akaviona vitambaa vya sanda vimelala </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>humo, lakini hakuingia. Simoni  Petro akaja nyuma yake, akaingia kaburini, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akaviona vitambaa vimelala humo, na kadhalika leso ya kufunikia kichwa chake, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hiyo imekunjwa, haikulala pamoja na vitambaa vingine, bali peke yake mahali pake.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo yule mfuasi mwingine aliyefika kwanza kaburini akaingia pia, akaona akasadiki.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana mpaka hapa walikuwa hawajafahamu bado Maandiko </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya kwamba imempasa kufufuka katika wafu.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana
(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>				</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA PASAKA MWAKA B"}],Guid:"Iq0mly43sEikPWQTB7Wz7g",
Text:"DOMINIKA ZA PASAKA MWAKA B"}